race.description: Trackside Pet Meats Pick 6 (N/P) Stake Pr2 Divisio
race.comment: SHANNY ROSE (1) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (23.64) at this track in a Grade 6. Looks suited here and big improvement expected. TRADING HALT (5) filled a minor placing last start at Murray Bridge behind Arrow Mac (22.93) in a Grade 6. Leading chance. COMPTON BOWIE (2) failed to come into contention last start after losing his position early at this track, but prior to that won by 2.75 lengths at this track (18.18) beating PATE BISCUIT in a TG1-4W on October 2. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Has ability and is one of the better chances. DIMORA BERNIE (7) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.
